Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.82,0:00:06.94,Chiha-poem,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Naniwa Bay, now the flower blooms, but for winter.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.64,0:00:11.28,Chiha-poem,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Here comes spring, now the flower blooms.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.49,0:00:18.65,Chiha-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Did you watch last night's episode?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.65,0:00:20.83,Chiha-main,B,0000,0000,0000,,Uh-huh, you bet!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.43,0:00:22.45,Chiha-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Have you heard?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.45,0:00:23.64,Chiha-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,One of the new students
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.64,0:00:25.88,Chiha-main,,0000,0000,0000,,is the younger sister of the model Ayase Chitose!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.88,0:00:27.50,Chiha-main,B,0000,0000,0000,,No way!  I'm a huge fan!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.50,0:00:29.27,Chiha-main,C,0000,0000,0000,,She must be super cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.27,0:00:29.79,Chiha-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.79,0:00:31.41,Chiha-main,B,0000,0000,0000,,Really?  Let's go check her out!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.41,0:00:32.02,Chiha-main,C,0000,0000,0000,,Which class?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.02,0:00:32.89,Chiha-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Class 2!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.89,0:00:35.26,Chiha-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,But she's usually in the lobby during lunch!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.87,0:00:40.85,Chiha-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.58,0:00:44.46,Chiha-note,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Please come see Ayase Chihaya in class 1-2!!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.42,0:00:45.67,Chiha-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Ayase Chihaya...?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.67,0:00:49.55,Chiha-note,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Let's start a competitive karuta club!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.12,0:00:47.93,Chiha-main,,0000,0000,0000,,A competitive karuta club?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.01,0:00:48.98,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.14,0:01:00.08,Chiha-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,E-Err...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.29,0:01:05.08,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,1, 2, 3, 4!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.23,0:01:07.10,Chiha-main,B,0000,0000,0000,,The hell?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.42,0:01:08.53,Chiha-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Track pants?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.53,0:01:10.34,Chiha-main,C,0000,0000,0000,,Look at the belt.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.86,0:01:12.21,Chiha-main,Teach,0000,0000,0000,,Ayase-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.59,0:01:14.59,Chiha-main,Teach,0000,0000,0000,,Just look at yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.59,0:01:16.11,Chiha-main,Teach,0000,0000,0000,,Have you no shame?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.11,0:01:17.16,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.16,0:01:19.80,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,You're the one who told me that\N I shouldn't do this with a skirt on.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.80,0:01:22.24,Chiha-main,Teach,0000,0000,0000,,If you're going to wear track pants,\N take off the skirt!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.24,0:01:25.22,Chiha-main,Teach,0000,0000,0000,,Also, you're only allowed to\N put one flyer on the board.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.70,0:01:28.13,Chiha-main,Teach,0000,0000,0000,,Don't take it off here!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.60,0:01:31.12,Chiha-overlap,Teach,0000,0000,0000,,You keep trying to start a karuta club,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.60,0:01:32.33,Chiha-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Right, everyone was saying how she's pretty,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.12,0:01:33.49,Chiha-overlap,Teach,0000,0000,0000,,but you always fall asleep during classical literature!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.33,0:01:35.06,Chiha-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,but it's wasted as soon as she talks or does something.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.06,0:01:36.56,Chiha-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Beauty in vain...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.45,0:01:44.75,Chiha-title,A,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1500,0)}Chihaya Furu
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.10,0:02:54.06,Chiha-ep-title-verse,EpTitle,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(900,800)}Verse 1
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.10,0:02:54.06,Chiha-ep-title-poem,EpTitle,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(900,800)}Now \NThe \NFlower \NBlooms
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.07,0:02:57.57,Chiha-note,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Let's start a competitive karuta club!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.63,0:02:57.57,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Nobody's come to see me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.34,0:03:00.57,Chiha-main,Horikawa,0000,0000,0000,,Chi-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.57,0:03:02.25,Chiha-main,Horikawa,0000,0000,0000,,Forget about karuta.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.25,0:03:04.55,Chiha-main,Horikawa,0000,0000,0000,,Do track with me again.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.55,0:03:06.19,Chiha-main,Horikawa,0000,0000,0000,,It'd be a waste to just quit
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.19,0:03:07.91,Chiha-main,,0000,0000,0000,,after qualifying for the \Ncity meet in short distance.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.91,0:03:10.54,Chiha-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Is karuta that idiom card game?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.99,0:03:12.33,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,It's not.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.89,0:03:17.31,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Track was just a way for me to meet people.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.31,0:03:18.55,Chiha-main,Horikawa,0000,0000,0000,,Meet people?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.55,0:03:20.02,Chiha-main,Horikawa,0000,0000,0000,,What's that supposed to mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.43,0:03:21.34,Chiha-overlap,A,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, we need to hurry to practice,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.34,0:03:22.96,Chiha-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,or the seniors will yell at us again.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.96,0:03:24.99,Chiha-main,Horikawa,0000,0000,0000,,Uh-huh.  See you later, Chi-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.43,0:03:26.80,Chiha-main,Horikawa,0000,0000,0000,,Wait up!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.80,0:03:27.84,Chiha-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Faster!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.84,0:03:28.85,Chiha-main,Horikawa,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.85,0:03:30.68,Chiha-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,That one senior is so scary!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.77,0:03:37.02,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,It must be nice to have teammates.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.04,0:03:43.37,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,I figured that high school was where I could
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.37,0:03:47.33,Chiha-internal,,0000,0000,0000,,find other players and focus 100% on karuta.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.47,0:03:58.83,Chiha-flashback,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,That makes you the Queen, Ayase-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.33,0:04:02.60,Chiha-poem,Voice,0000,0000,0000,,None are left who know me
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.60,0:04:04.82,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Back when I really enjoyed karuta...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.82,0:04:06.82,Chiha-poem,Voice,0000,0000,0000,,Takasago pines...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.16,0:04:11.29,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,They call you "beauty in vain"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.29,0:04:12.85,Chiha-main,,0000,0000,0000,,because you just plop yourself on the ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.85,0:04:15.64,Chiha-poem,Voice,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...can never replace them.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.64,0:04:16.36,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Chihaya.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.23,0:04:21.38,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Taichi?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.14,0:04:24.60,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,That's awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.60,0:04:26.82,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,I never thought you'd come to this high school.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.82,0:04:31.22,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,I figured you would stay at \Nthat fancy academy for high school with the free ride.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.22,0:04:33.39,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,And spend three more years commuting
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.39,0:04:35.17,Chiha-main,,0000,0000,0000,,an hour and a half each way?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.47,0:04:36.71,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, that hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.00,0:04:39.28,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, I think it's more surprising
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.28,0:04:41.34,Chiha-main,,0000,0000,0000,,that you made it into a good public school.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.22,0:04:48.59,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Taichi, you've grown taller.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.53,0:04:51.19,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,But we're practically the same height!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.19,0:04:52.14,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get too cocky!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.14,0:04:53.56,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,I'm still gonna grow!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.92,0:04:55.23,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,As am I.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.23,0:04:56.31,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,You can stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.34,0:04:59.15,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Taichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.65,0:05:01.98,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.98,0:05:03.18,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Taichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.76,0:05:06.00,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Taichi!  Taichi!  Taichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.00,0:05:07.61,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.61,0:05:09.76,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Chihaya, you probably aren't \Nvery popular with the guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.90,0:05:23.96,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Chihaya.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.96,0:05:24.72,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.63,0:05:26.56,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Say...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.85,0:05:31.72,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me for a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.17,0:05:34.02,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, it's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.88,0:05:35.82,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.82,0:05:36.73,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,I'm at the station.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.30,0:05:39.98,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, not yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.69,0:05:43.95,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?  You're waiting at Bubaigawara?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.36,0:05:45.93,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Fine, fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.93,0:05:46.82,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,I'm hanging up.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.47,0:05:52.37,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Your girlfriend?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.74,0:05:54.50,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,You have a girlfriend?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.00,0:05:56.52,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Am I not allowed to have one?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.44,0:05:58.92,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.24,0:06:01.41,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.85,0:06:02.99,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.33,0:06:04.48,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Was it that big of a shock?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.09,0:06:05.91,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.91,0:06:09.74,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,W-Well, I'm only with her\N because she asked me out.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.74,0:06:11.39,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not really attached to her or anything...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.82,0:06:17.01,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe Arata's found something more important to him than karuta.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.37,0:06:18.18,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.46,0:06:22.75,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,What's that supposed to mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.03,0:06:24.97,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Taichi?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.88,0:06:31.24,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Have you been in touch with Arata?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.78,0:06:35.23,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,No, I didn't get a New Year's card from him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.63,0:06:39.67,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Arata wasn't in last year's national tournament.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.21,0:06:43.67,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,I was on the track team in middle school,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.67,0:06:47.02,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,so I've never been to the Omi Jingu tournament.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.02,0:06:49.26,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing wrong with track.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.26,0:06:49.76,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.25,0:06:53.14,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,I'm planning on doing \Nsomething else in high school.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.14,0:06:54.68,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Karuta was just a hobby.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.68,0:06:57.17,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,What?  You're not gonna play karuta?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.46,0:06:59.78,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,We're even in the same high school!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.78,0:07:02.72,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,I spent most of my time in\N middle school playing soccer.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.72,0:07:04.65,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,We're not gonna play karuta forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.20,0:07:10.47,Chiha-poem,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,None are left who know me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.27,0:07:15.82,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,This poem was about losing old friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.91,0:07:19.51,Chiha-flashback,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,As long as we keep playing,\N we'll see each other again!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.17,0:07:21.59,Chiha-flashback,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,I just know it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.89,0:07:33.15,Chiha-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Chi-chan!  Hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.15,0:07:34.74,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Wait for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.73,0:07:42.10,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Three years ago, in Tokyo,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.15,0:07:45.77,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,before I found my passion...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.46,0:07:48.20,Chiha-main,B,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.20,0:07:50.55,Chiha-main,B,0000,0000,0000,,How did your sister do in the beauty pageant?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.55,0:07:54.11,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, she made it to the final round,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.22,0:07:58.52,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,and her picture will be in the newspaper tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.52,0:08:00.09,Chiha-main,C,0000,0000,0000,,Really?  That's amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.09,0:08:01.71,Chiha-main,D,0000,0000,0000,,I wanna see!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.71,0:08:04.08,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Chihaya's sister is really pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.24,0:08:06.45,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Yep.  Don't you agree, Taichi?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.45,0:08:08.46,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.  She's the opposite of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.58,0:08:11.36,Chiha-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Hilarious!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.75,0:08:14.06,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Aw, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.06,0:08:16.12,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Reflexes are the one area you can match me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.12,0:08:17.46,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Don't forget height.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.46,0:08:19.01,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!  You wanna make something of it, Chihaya?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.01,0:08:19.93,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.34,0:08:27.85,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.30,0:08:34.91,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,That transfer student never talks.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.22,0:08:36.57,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.57,0:08:38.66,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,It seems he doesn't have any friends, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.95,0:08:41.33,Chiha-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,You should probably stay away from him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.33,0:08:43.61,Chiha-main,B,0000,0000,0000,,I've heard that he snacks on bugs.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.61,0:08:44.92,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,What?  For real?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.92,0:08:46.25,Chiha-main,B,0000,0000,0000,,Someone from Class 2 saw it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.25,0:08:47.75,Chiha-main,C,0000,0000,0000,,He has holes in his socks, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.75,0:08:49.75,Chiha-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,We don't need him in our class.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.08,0:08:51.37,Chiha-main,B,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Chi-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.37,0:08:51.76,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.76,0:08:52.85,Chiha-main,B,0000,0000,0000,,Look at this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.85,0:08:55.94,Chiha-main,B,0000,0000,0000,,We've been taking notes on \NWataya-kun's Fukui dialect.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.70,0:08:59.99,Chiha-note,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,Wataya Lexicon\NHay, hay -> Hey, hey\NYah, yah -> Yeah, yeah\NStick it -> No idea\NLez -> Let's\NCanker -> ??
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.94,0:08:58.14,Chiha-main,C,0000,0000,0000,,But he doesn't talk much these days.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.14,0:08:59.04,Chiha-main,C,0000,0000,0000,,We can't add to the list.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.04,0:09:00.01,Chiha-main,C,0000,0000,0000,,He doesn't wanna share.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.14,0:09:02.05,Chiha-main,B,0000,0000,0000,,I know...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.05,0:09:03.52,Chiha-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Then, the other day...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.86,0:09:05.89,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,If I were in Wataya-kun's shoes,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.24,0:09:08.12,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't want to talk to people who kept
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.12,0:09:09.77,Chiha-main,,0000,0000,0000,,taking notes just so they could laugh at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.03,0:09:16.08,Chiha-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,That wasn't our intention.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.08,0:09:16.78,Chiha-main,B,0000,0000,0000,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.06,0:09:18.64,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, really?  Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.64,0:09:20.38,Chiha-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Nah, it's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.38,0:09:21.04,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.55,0:09:39.36,Chiha-main,Man,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you forgot your directions.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.36,0:09:40.49,Chiha-main,Man,0000,0000,0000,,You'll need this.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.79,0:09:41.60,Chiha-main,Arata,0000,0000,0000,,I memorized it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.83,0:09:43.17,Chiha-main,Man,0000,0000,0000,,You memorized it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.17,0:09:44.43,Chiha-main,Man,0000,0000,0000,,This is your first day!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.43,0:09:45.36,Chiha-main,Man,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.36,0:09:47.03,Chiha-main,Man,0000,0000,0000,,You have 200 stops!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.51,0:09:49.14,Chiha-main,Man,0000,0000,0000,,Don't make any mistakes!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.56,0:09:52.91,Chiha-internal,Arata,0000,0000,0000,,Area 2, District 5.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.91,0:09:54.88,Chiha-internal,Arata,0000,0000,0000,,Fujiwara, plus five across the street.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.88,0:09:57.65,Chiha-internal,Arata,0000,0000,0000,,Osawa, Fujimiya, Yamamoto...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.65,0:09:59.45,Chiha-internal,Arata,0000,0000,0000,,Uchiyama's subscription was canceled.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.45,0:10:00.71,Chiha-internal,Arata,0000,0000,0000,,Yokota Cooperative.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.71,0:10:03.87,Chiha-internal,Arata,0000,0000,0000,,101, 103, 203, 204.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.89,0:10:11.92,Chiha-internal,Arata,0000,0000,0000,,Next is Ayase.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.68,0:10:24.10,Chiha-main,Arata,0000,0000,0000,,G-Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.10,0:10:24.85,Chiha-main,Chihaya,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.29,0:10:36.59,Chiha-main,Chihaya,0000,0000,0000,,Sis!  Sis!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.59,0:10:37.48,Chiha-main,Chihaya,0000,0000,0000,,You're in the paper!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.48,0:10:38.50,Chiha-main,Chihaya,0000,0000,0000,,Wake up!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.32,0:10:43.58,newspaper,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}Japan Sports Paper
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.32,0:10:43.58,newspaper,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Japan's Most\N Beautiful Girl \NGrand Prix
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.32,0:10:43.58,13,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,13 Years Old
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.63,0:10:42.27,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Look!  There's your picture!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.27,0:10:43.58,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Right here!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.28,0:10:47.66,Chiha-main,Chitose,0000,0000,0000,,As a footnote.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.18,0:10:49.42,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Why is that bad?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.42,0:10:52.49,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,It's amazing that you made it to the final fifteen!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.49,0:10:54.80,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Can I have this picture?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.80,0:10:56.05,Chiha-main,Chitose,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.06,0:11:01.52,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,The winner has a better body, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.80,0:11:06.60,Chiha-main,Chitose,0000,0000,0000,,You always say the first thing \Nthat comes into your head!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.84,0:11:08.62,Chiha-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Chi-chan, I saw the paper!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.62,0:11:10.20,Chiha-main,B,0000,0000,0000,,Your sister's amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.20,0:11:12.02,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Yep!  She's amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.02,0:11:14.37,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, she's really in the paper.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.37,0:11:15.67,Chiha-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Your sister's so pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.67,0:11:16.67,Chiha-main,B,0000,0000,0000,,Wow...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.67,0:11:18.53,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, the two of you might be sisters,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.53,0:11:21.24,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,but you still look like a boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.93,0:11:27.04,Chiha-main,Teach,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.43,0:11:29.14,Chiha-main,Teach,0000,0000,0000,,Sit down.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.54,0:11:32.79,Chiha-note,Teach,0000,0000,0000,,Hundred Poet Memorization Sheet
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.04,0:11:32.79,Chiha-main,Teach,0000,0000,0000,,Did everyone fill out their Hundred Poet sheet with stickers?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.09,0:11:35.82,Chiha-main,Teach,0000,0000,0000,,If you memorize all one hundred poems,\N you should take the test.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.82,0:11:37.15,Chiha-overlap,Teach,0000,0000,0000,,We'll have the students who've
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.82,0:11:37.59,Chiha-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think so.  How many did you memorize?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.15,0:11:40.02,Chiha-overlap,,0000,0000,0000,,learned their poems participate in the karuta tournament.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.66,0:11:39.18,Chiha-main,B,0000,0000,0000,,Only ten.  What about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.05,0:11:40.91,Chiha-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Fifteen.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.91,0:11:42.43,Chiha-main,B,0000,0000,0000,,Same difference.  \NDon't be such a snob.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.43,0:11:44.52,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Chihaya, how many did you memorize?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.52,0:11:46.95,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Only half, I think...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.00,0:11:50.68,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, yeah.  \NYou're a better student than I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.06,0:11:53.55,Chiha-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Mashima-kun, you've already\N memorized all of them?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.55,0:11:54.43,Chiha-main,B,0000,0000,0000,,That was quick.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.43,0:11:55.96,Chiha-main,B,0000,0000,0000,,You can do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.96,0:11:57.57,Chiha-main,Teach,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, quiet down!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.95,0:12:00.12,Chiha-main,Teach,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, Mashima-kun isn't the only person
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.12,0:12:03.80,Chiha-main,,0000,0000,0000,,in the class who memorized\N all one hundred poems.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.23,0:12:05.41,Chiha-main,Teach,0000,0000,0000,,The other person is...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.99,0:12:07.38,Chiha-main,Teach,0000,0000,0000,,Wataya-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.38,0:12:08.71,Chiha-main,BG,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.30,0:12:12.61,Chiha-main,Teach,0000,0000,0000,,Wataya-kun took the test\N after school yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.61,0:12:14.82,Chiha-main,Teach,0000,0000,0000,,He got all 100 poems on the first try.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.82,0:12:16.27,Chiha-main,,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.28,0:12:16.27,Chiha-overlap,,0000,0000,0000,,Round of applause!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.27,0:12:17.50,Chiha-main,,0000,0000,0000,,Really? In one go?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.05,0:12:20.76,Chiha-main,Teach,0000,0000,0000,,Will you participate in the\N karuta tournament next month?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.66,0:12:23.26,Chiha-main,Arata,0000,0000,0000,,Uh... yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.87,0:12:24.67,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.33,0:12:28.18,Chiha-main,Arata,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Good morning.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.79,0:12:31.27,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,The paper boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.40,0:12:32.67,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,I remember now!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.67,0:12:35.51,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,You delivered our paper this morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.51,0:12:36.77,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,That's amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.77,0:12:38.65,Chiha-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Paper boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.65,0:12:40.85,Chiha-main,B,0000,0000,0000,,Grade schoolers aren't\N supposed to be working.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.85,0:12:43.49,Chiha-main,Teach,0000,0000,0000,,Um, Wataya-kun? \N Is this true?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.73,0:12:48.28,Chiha-main,Arata,0000,0000,0000,,I help out from time \Nto time when I'm asked.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.73,0:12:50.25,Chiha-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,He must be poor.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.25,0:12:52.95,Chiha-main,B,0000,0000,0000,,Doesn't he wear the same pants every day?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.23,0:12:57.58,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Taichi.  Isn't Wataya-kun amazing?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.12,0:12:59.76,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,He's delivering the newspaper!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.21,0:13:02.87,Chiha-main,Teach,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, quiet down.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.87,0:13:05.55,Chiha-main,Teach,0000,0000,0000,,Everybody should try their best to\N memorize all one hundred poems.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.48,0:13:22.84,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Wataya-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.08,0:13:30.88,Chiha-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Bye, Mashima-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.88,0:13:31.72,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.77,0:13:43.30,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.30,0:13:45.72,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.89,0:13:52.68,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, oops!  Sorry about\N ruining your only pair of pants!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.99,0:13:53.81,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Taichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.16,0:13:56.34,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Don't have anything to wear tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.34,0:13:58.31,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,You can borrow your mom's skirt...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.99,0:14:03.03,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't think you were such a mean person!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.95,0:14:08.45,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Well, why do you keep taking his side?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.45,0:14:11.44,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone's gonna start ignoring you tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.81,0:14:12.37,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.45,0:14:15.00,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna ignore you, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.00,0:14:15.91,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,I mean it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.91,0:14:16.87,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,I said that I don't care!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.12,0:14:23.38,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Don't come crying to me later!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.38,0:14:24.51,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,You'll pay for this!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.75,0:14:39.23,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, this place is falling apart.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.55,0:14:40.27,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.27,0:14:41.61,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Umm, sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.91,0:14:44.48,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,I always say the first thing\N that comes into my head!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.48,0:14:47.28,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,That's why my sister \Nkicked me this morning...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.60,0:14:50.86,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,U-Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.38,0:14:53.87,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,You know, you can talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.87,0:14:55.81,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not taking notes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.73,0:15:02.38,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,It's freezing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.08,0:15:04.38,Chiha-main,Arata,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Why...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.71,0:15:11.09,Chiha-main,Arata,0000,0000,0000,,Why were you waiting for\N the newspaper this morning?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.31,0:15:13.77,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He spoke!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.49,0:15:17.44,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,My sister was in a beauty pageant,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.44,0:15:19.53,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,and I couldn't wait to see the article!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.53,0:15:20.50,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Look, right here!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.50,0:15:22.25,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,My sister's in the back!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.56,0:15:24.11,Chiha-main,Arata,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, that's really something.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.45,0:15:26.36,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't she pretty? \NIsn't she awesome?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.02,0:15:31.23,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,My dream is to see my sister\N become the top model in Japan!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.82,0:15:36.24,Chiha-main,Arata,0000,0000,0000,,You can't call that a dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.43,0:15:42.00,Chiha-main,Arata,0000,0000,0000,,Your dream should be about yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.85,0:15:44.45,Chiha-main,Arata,0000,0000,0000,,Don't take someone else's.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.76,0:15:46.41,Chiha-main,Arata,0000,0000,0000,,That wouldn't be fair to your sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.83,0:15:49.23,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.23,0:15:51.42,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have a dream, Wataya-kun?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.42,0:15:52.69,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Your own dream?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.79,0:16:05.61,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.61,0:16:07.26,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't this Hundred Poets?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.74,0:16:09.64,Chiha-main,Arata,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know how to play?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.64,0:16:14.16,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Well, we have a karuta tournament\N at our school every year.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.16,0:16:15.74,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,You know, the one the teacher mentioned.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.42,0:16:16.41,Chiha-overlap,Arata,0000,0000,0000,,L-Lez play!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.76,0:16:17.49,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.49,0:16:18.39,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.39,0:16:19.34,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.34,0:16:21.08,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,I'll play, but we need someone to do the reading.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.10,0:16:24.08,Chiha-main,Arata,0000,0000,0000,,I have a tape for that!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.99,0:16:26.07,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.53,0:16:28.25,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Why is he so excited?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.09,0:16:34.09,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Um...  How does this work?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.06,0:16:38.10,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Line up 25 cards in 3 rows.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.24,0:16:41.30,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,When the first verse of a poem is read,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.30,0:16:43.88,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,you grab the card with the second verse.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.36,0:16:49.11,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,I've only memorized around 50 poems...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.91,0:16:52.61,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it's just a game.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.68,0:16:59.79,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,What was that look?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.56,0:17:01.94,Chiha-main,Arata,0000,0000,0000,,Shall we begin?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.94,0:17:02.49,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.90,0:17:04.24,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.21,0:17:15.63,Chiha-poem,N,0000,0000,0000,,The storm...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.18,0:17:16.93,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.38,0:17:20.23,Chiha-main,Arata,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, oops.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.65,0:17:30.20,Chiha-poem,N,0000,0000,0000,,to set the Tatsuta River ablaze
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.89,0:17:29.90,Chiha-card-TS,N,0000,0000,0000,,to set the Tatsuta River ablaze
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.20,0:17:31.87,Chiha-main,Arata,0000,0000,0000,,Another card got stuck.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.82,0:17:43.84,Chiha-poem,N,0000,0000,0000,,May I live to see the day when
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.16,0:17:46.92,Chiha-card-TS,N,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1400,0)}when the fisherman who \Ncasts his nets can seem dear
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.94,0:17:51.27,Chiha-poem,N,0000,0000,0000,,The world offers no change, I pray,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.27,0:17:48.02,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,H-Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.02,0:17:49.14,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.26,0:17:55.01,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Is this how you play karuta?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.84,0:17:58.64,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,He's fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.37,0:18:00.26,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.02,0:18:01.92,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,So fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.82,0:18:05.08,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,I'm mad.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.60,0:18:08.00,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really mad.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.36,0:18:12.36,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,I should at least be able to take one card...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.04,0:18:17.61,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.61,0:18:23.62,Chiha-card-TS,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(900,0)}are joined at river's end
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.44,0:18:20.55,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,I know the first verse for that card.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.55,0:18:23.62,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,"Swift waters parted by the jagged rocks"
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.86,0:18:26.50,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,One card.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.55,0:18:29.50,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,It's just one card.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.75,0:18:31.80,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,I have to get it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.07,0:18:41.83,Chiha-poem,N,0000,0000,0000,,Swift...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.04,0:18:52.56,Chiha-poem,N,0000,0000,0000,,...waters parted by the jagged rocks
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.06,0:18:52.56,Chiha-card-TS,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,are joined at river's end
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.13,0:18:55.10,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,I did it! I got a card!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.10,0:18:57.54,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,I beat Wataya-kun to a card!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.10,0:19:01.57,Chiha-main,Arata,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.81,0:19:04.05,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,What happened?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.05,0:19:05.49,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,You're too good!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.49,0:19:07.48,Chiha-main,Arata,0000,0000,0000,,But you were able to take a card.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.48,0:19:10.14,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Only one card!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.64,0:19:13.84,Chiha-main,Arata,0000,0000,0000,,B-But, I had fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.56,0:19:18.58,Chiha-main,Arata,0000,0000,0000,,In Fukui, everyone played karuta.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.91,0:19:21.98,Chiha-main,Arata,0000,0000,0000,,That's not the case in Tokyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.36,0:19:24.35,Chiha-main,Arata,0000,0000,0000,,I usually play by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.72,0:19:26.85,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,By yourself?!  \NWhile listening to the tape?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.85,0:19:36.00,Chiha-card-TS,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,1800)}the red that is \Nthe Tatsuta River
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.75,0:19:33.72,Chiha-main,Arata,0000,0000,0000,,Karuta isn't very popular in other countries.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.17,0:19:36.00,Chiha-main,Arata,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it's not an easy game.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.87,0:19:39.36,Chiha-main,Arata,0000,0000,0000,,But that means...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.61,0:19:43.78,Chiha-main,Arata,0000,0000,0000,,If you become the best player in Japan,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.78,0:19:45.99,Chiha-main,Arata,0000,0000,0000,,you'll be the best in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.99,0:19:51.75,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,The best in the world?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.66,0:19:55.00,Chiha-main,Arata,0000,0000,0000,,My dream is to become
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.39,0:19:56.71,Chiha-main,Arata,0000,0000,0000,,a karuta master.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.25,0:19:59.76,Chiha-card-TS,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,are joined at river's end
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.32,0:19:59.47,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Master...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.17,0:20:03.30,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Dream...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.26,0:20:09.52,Chiha-card-TS,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,the red that is the Tatsuta River
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.10,0:20:09.52,Chiha-main,Arata,0000,0000,0000,,Chihaya is a good name.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.99,0:20:10.61,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.90,0:20:13.41,Chiha-main,Arata,0000,0000,0000,,Look, this is your card.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.77,0:20:22.09,Chiha-card-TS,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,the red that is the Tatsuta River
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.83,0:20:17.98,Chiha-main,Arata,0000,0000,0000,,The first verse for this card begins with Chihaya Furu (Impassionate). {makes more sense to me to leave this in the sub itself -tly}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.36,0:20:20.15,Chiha-main,Arata,0000,0000,0000,,This is the card you pick up when you hear Chihaya,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.15,0:20:22.10,Chiha-main,Arata,0000,0000,0000,,so in my mind, it's the Chihaya card.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.73,0:20:27.03,Chiha-main,Arata,0000,0000,0000,,That's how I see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.12,0:20:31.53,Chiha-main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,I'm home!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.53,0:20:32.18,Chiha-main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.66,0:20:34.33,Chiha-main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Arata, is this a friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.33,0:20:36.35,Chiha-main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, a girlfriend?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.35,0:20:37.17,Chiha-main,Arata,0000,0000,0000,,Mom...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.19,0:20:44.01,Chiha-card-TS,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,2000)}the red that is the Tatsuta River
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.41,0:20:39.91,Chiha-main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Arata's girlfriend, would you like some yams?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.91,0:20:41.24,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,No, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.77,0:20:51.33,Chiha-poem,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Impassionate gods have never seen
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.21,0:20:55.35,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,He was so fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.21,0:21:02.28,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,His dream...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.60,0:21:07.91,Chiha-poem,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,the red that is the Tatsuta River
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.83,0:21:12.36,Chiha-flashback,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,On the day I first played karuta with Arata,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.83,0:21:14.04,Chiha-card-TS,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,the red that is the Tatsuta River
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.83,0:21:17.31,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,I learned about more than just karuta.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.31,0:21:21.30,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,I discovered Arata's passion!
